---
---
<section class="relative min-h-[90vh] flex items-center justify-center overflow-hidden py-20 px-6">
  <div class="absolute inset-0 flex items-center justify-center pointer-events-none opacity-25 z-0">
    <svg class="w-[800px] h-[800px] text-vedicIndigo animate-spin-slow" viewBox="0 0 200 200" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="0.5">
      <circle cx="100" cy="100" r="90" />
      <circle cx="100" cy="100" r="60" />
      <circle cx="100" cy="100" r="30" />
      <polygon points="100,10 178,150 22,150" stroke="#00C8FF" stroke-width="0.3"/>
      <polygon points="100,190 22,50 178,50" stroke="#D4A017" stroke-width="0.3"/>
      <circle cx="100" cy="100" r="5" fill="currentColor"/>
    </svg>
  </div>

  <div class="max-w-5xl mx-auto text-center relative z-10 flex flex-col items-center">
    <div class="inline-flex items-center gap-2 px-3 py-1 border border-electricBlue/30 bg-electricBlue/10 backdrop-blur-sm text-electricBlue text-xs font-mono uppercase tracking-widest rounded-full mb-8 animate-pulse">
      <span class="w-1.5 h-1.5 rounded-full bg-electricBlue"></span>
      Broadcast Live Since 11 June 2026
    </div>

    <h1 class="font-display text-5xl md:text-8xl font-bold tracking-tight mb-6 leading-tight">
      Ancient Wisdom.<br />
      <span class="text-transparent bg-clip-text bg-gradient-to-r from-sacredGold via-electricBlue to-lotusWhite">
        Modern Code.
      </span>
    </h1>

    <p class="max-w-2xl text-base md:text-lg text-lotusWhite/70 font-light leading-relaxed tracking-wide mb-12">
      An architectural evolution in tech education. Decoding deep programming frameworks, cinematic engineering layouts, and advanced computing patterns without the fluff.
    </p>

    <div class="flex flex-col sm:flex-row items-center gap-6">
      <a 
        href="#modules" 
        class="w-full sm:w-auto px-8 py-4 bg-transparent border border-electricBlue text-electricBlue font-semibold text-xs tracking-widest uppercase hover:bg-electricBlue hover:text-cosmicBlack transition-all duration-300 shadow-[0_0_30px_rgba(0,200,255,0.1)] hover:shadow-[0_0_40px_rgba(0,200,255,0.3)]"
      >
        Explore Syllabus
      </a>
      <a 
        href="#philosophy" 
        class="w-full sm:w-auto px-8 py-4 text-lotusWhite/60 hover:text-lotusWhite font-semibold text-xs tracking-widest uppercase transition-all duration-300 flex items-center justify-center gap-2"
      >
        The Manifesto <span class="text-sacredGold">→</span>
      </a>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
